{"tid":1884212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特別任務@17 Feb】 維多C 贊助 CCTVB後生仔(40歲)傾吓偈","createTime":"2020-02-17T12:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T23:31:54.000Z","uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"02b6e86d42ccc61ca60c6fdd288c80f67b6b9af3","tid":1884212,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【特別任務@17 Feb】<br />\n💎維多C X 後生仔傾吓偈💎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RedoxonHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRedoxonHK%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=c798e6f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RedoxonHK/</a><br />\n👆👆👆去派嬲再留言👆👆👆</div><br />\n<br />\n原來維多C 係後生仔傾吓偈呢個妖言惑眾節目嘅贊助商，梗係要抵制啦！🤟🏻<br />\n唔好意思，小編呢排忙，遲出咗呢個任務🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n成年人建議每日攝取維他命C為90毫克，叫人冲2000毫克嚟飲？飲一杯就已經達到攝取上限喇！小朋友飲仲會超標添！如果之後再食蔬果，長期食過量維他命C咪有機會腎衰歇？🥵<br />\n<br />\n其實對於預防流感，維他命C的影響極細！做運動同均衡飲食好過啦！咪益無良藥廠！😊<br />\n[Source]<br />\n急補維他命C 有效抗流感？ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ruYGg3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ruYGg3&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5b07f6ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2ruYGg3</a><br />\n----------------------<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">📌【TVB春袋: 廣告商抵制名單】📌<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻 電子ver <a href=\"http://bit.ly/tvbadver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftvbadver&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=ebbb7abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/tvbadver</a> 👈🏻<br />\n👉🏻 文宣ver <a href=\"http://bit.ly/tvbposter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftvbposter&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=50447e63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/tvbposter</a> 👈🏻</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">⚠️抵制TVB戰線 @sayno2tvb<br />\nTG群: @Sayno2cctvb<br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://www.fb.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=0b9c8817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.fb.com/sayno2tvb</a></div></span></span>"},{"pid":"6d2e7bedd91b0ef49d416ffcec532addd54182e6","tid":1884212,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">特別任務@17 Feb】<br />\n💎維多C X 後生仔傾吓偈💎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RedoxonHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRedoxonHK%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbNOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=c798e6f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RedoxonHK/</a><br />\n👆👆👆去派嬲再留言👆👆👆</div>"},{"pid":"220d6af654927896fd2856074b6d15cdc363357c","tid":1884212,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81848cf76914ec9f914cc65471954eb2428e5370","tid":1884212,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e787cab03108075e4df1589f91cc98fefbdccd","tid":1884212,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"空氣推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbfe12b760a5a9cf4269be49c1a099ce95193b9","tid":1884212,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef09e2b2c7d89389730361f98c44627e7521db8","tid":1884212,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa